::Aerotaur::
       He had in fact not heard Windlord and continued on his way.  He landed 
at the cave where they had stayed not so long ago and worked his way inside 
to rest his wings.  "I'm sorry my friend, but this is the way it must be."  
He said it outloud though no one was there to hear him.
